messageBody:
Have you had a chance to cast your eye over it yet?
I'd really like to get the proposal posted, its icon is starting to
glare at me.
We've had two or three eyes on it so I think this is more or less what
we want.
I'm still a bit worried that I may have made it too essay-like, what do
you think?

Michael Everson wrote:
>
> At 14:29 +0100 2007-09-22, amd64_hacker wrote:
> >I spotted and corrected a few typos in the proposal last week.
> >
> >If no one has any improvements/suggestions/objections then I'll email
> >the proposal on the 1st of October.
>
> I've been travelling for three weeks (two weeks in Indonesia and
> Singapore doing Javanese and Batak and one week in China at WG2). I'm
> in Singapore Airport now. For my part I won't get to review the
> contribution for at least 5 days.
> --
> Michael Everson * http://www.evertype.com <http://www.evertype.com>
>
>
